Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我緊緊地纏繞的話不行喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:58.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:03.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.19,0:22:09.37,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.53,0:22:15.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.87,0:22:28.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.72,0:22:39.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.43,0:22:47.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能  太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.24,0:23:03.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.93,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是不可思議的關鍵鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.71,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室中的驚人手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.76,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得就在這附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是叫「光莊」啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.27,0:01:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一棟就像要倒的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會就是這裡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中鑰匙密室事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.20,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今年春天這裡就重新改建了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道有這麼回事 害我嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.33,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你讀書的時候住的地方完全不一樣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 天壤之別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是因為討厭囉嗦的房東的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前就不租了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這回事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己一個人住在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 孩子們都到很遠的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在有個孫子和我住在同樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣婆婆就不會無聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城南大學唸建築 不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近常常把自己關在房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他怎麼回事 他也不肯講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想身為名偵探的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能問出什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳才會打電話給我啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說八點左右會來這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四樓是我和孫子住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樓到三樓全部租給別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用備用鑰匙開門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎？ 擅自開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 這是我孫子的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真 出去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是邋遢的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.98,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是蠟筆而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中紀念碑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水裡面有一隻鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真 振作一點 阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷左手的動脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有其他的刀痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 叫城戶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.08,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是住在樓下的醫學系學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是阿真的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你孫子已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管 快去叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生…好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是喝醉酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生 阿真先生出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是宗田真先生 二十二歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是城南大學工學院建築系四年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是割斷手腕動脈出血過多而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從他死後頸部的僵硬程度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多已經死了二、三個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.69,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說推定死亡時間是下午六點到七點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自殺不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿真先生製造的建築模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水池裡面有隻鑰匙是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是玄關的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且經過特殊製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容易複製
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且備份鑰匙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光江婆婆跟管理員各有一隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到達的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關的鎖呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鎖住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才判斷是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真不會自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下午拿果汁過來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還說晚餐想吃南瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幾點鐘呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是五點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到阿真就這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那個果汁是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我特製的 能止渴的果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一杯有蜂蜜蒜頭香蕉的果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之那時候一點異樣都看不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那孩子沒有理由會自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真他很煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的畢業專題研究報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行得不是很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會悶悶不樂吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.64,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有看到房間那些蠟筆亂畫和這房間的佈置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他的心情很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鑰匙上面的白色東西是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是衛生紙吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛生紙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是紙巾或是其他的紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算濕了也不會那麼容易就溶解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是將衛生紙剪成條狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後做成繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.67,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 鑰匙上面為什麼要弄這個東西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.72,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 他的個性是有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是興趣的問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這間房間是密室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣窗是打開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小的縫隙 你想人可以穿來穿去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 氣窗的縫隙只有十五公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的窗戶都被鎖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這是一間完整的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是覺得他不是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.47,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑漆漆的地方無法正確的割到動脈吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑漆漆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們進來的時候沒有燈光嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過浴室就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也是沒亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我開燈之後再進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死亡推定時間的下午六點到七點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的天還沒有黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是浴室那裡沒有窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有開燈之下要準確對準手腕是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.29,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是犯人在犯案後將燈給關掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那牆壁這些蠟筆畫應該就是犯人故意畫上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在剩下鑰匙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.88,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是如何將鑰匙放進水中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩個疑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼犯人將那條柱子和門把上 不像牆壁一樣亂畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是整齊的一條線呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那氣窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.03,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像犯人沒有注意到那邊早就被打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開的不只是那個氣窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收回前言 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個他殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解開這把戲的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個信箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一條線連接在模型上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後拉到玄關那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從信箱將線拉出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用鑰匙上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將鑰匙放入一邊的線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將另外一條線慢慢拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙就會慢慢往房間方向過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到模型的水中的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛生紙遇水就斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就掉到水裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣謎底就解開了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 不愧是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 所以才會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 我有點不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個玄關到客廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個直角方向吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是從這裡把線拉到客廳的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.41,0:13:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會在那條柱子上面留下痕跡的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人故意在柱子上面塗上蠟筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓人知道他不是利用線去作案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.13,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是直接從信箱將大門的鎖給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 氣窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那種手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是利用氣窗來完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是有可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 那裡有一隻狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是隻很盡責的看門狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了家人之外 看到其他人都會叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 城戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常被它吠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.29,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院那裡一片空曠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人在那裡做奇怪動作的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會吠的更大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來果然是自殺 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他是被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且犯人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者的傷口只有一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點其他傷痕也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀就狠狠地割了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這麼準確做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有醫學觀念的人才做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是利用什麼方法呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關那邊的上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個房間都是蠟筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.96,0:14:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.22,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會將那個窗戶稍微打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成一個似是而非的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只剩下證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從這裡傳出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.87,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老婆婆裝果汁的杯子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇 阿真竟然會洗杯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.02,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣證據就有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道犯人是用什麼方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 真的嗎？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在做給你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆 鑰匙借我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你怎麼可能會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 鑰匙就行了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問這麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我出去之後將燈給關掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我們第一次進來的時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開始了 大家要安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神氣什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有東西掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雄性甲蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是路燈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是犯人使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你為什麼用甲蟲呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這紀念品的塔頂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾有雌性甲蟲的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋪在玄關那邊的上衣是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.86,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了讓甲蟲方便行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人特地放的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平地或是光滑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲就很難移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的走廊和客廳都鋪著地毯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 這裡的環境有利於犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才的甲蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪裡拿來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自將城戶先生家裡面養的甲蟲給拿來用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了一隻 對不起 城戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我去叫你之前 你進過這個房間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒進來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 你為什麼這樣問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.05,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼城戶先生的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有老婆婆特製的果汁的味道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆拿果汁過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晚上五點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.81,0:19:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把阿真先生他喝過的杯子洗過了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用自己的手帕將滴在地上的果汁給擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄性甲蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起雌性甲蟲的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它反而會被果汁強烈的味道給吸引過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到紀念品以外的地方去就麻煩了 對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.78,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是將雌性的甲蟲體液擦在這紀念品的塔頂吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把手帕拿出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈了這個局把他殺了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘記把手巾處理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喝慶功酒睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要殺害阿真先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.02,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他提議從大學醫院將安眠藥給偷出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後賣出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果現在他卻說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說今晚你會過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他洩漏了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後果可不堪設想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想阿真他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是後悔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會不想再繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在講這些已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你想像中的還要寶貴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在監獄裡面好好的反省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.46,0:21:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花上你的大半人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光江婆婆真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.98,0:23:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能代替阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.03,0:23:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有空就過去看看她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今晚的柯南真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我非常驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.62,0:23:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時都在叔叔旁邊聽著他那些名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的「耳濡目染」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託我的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你在不知不覺中學會如何做一個出色的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.21,0:23:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔最好多多學習怎麼做一個出色的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕真兇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找 快把高木和佐藤給找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.02,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.89,0:23:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要調查東田先生在案發之前最後去過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那間居酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.36,0:24:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.51,0:24:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個房間是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也住在這公寓裡面吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.86,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.16,0:24:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事戀愛物語２(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士的新發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.25,0:24:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回是戀愛物語２
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.91,0:24:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐藤警官和我的戀愛物語嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.48,0:24:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣 我一定橫刀奪愛
